high_descs: Turn left the head to the shelf on your right
Pick up the dirty cloth on the left side
Turn right then head to the sink
Put the dirty cloth and rinse it in the sink
Turn left facing the toilet tank
Put the clean cloth on the tank beside the toilet tissue
anns.task_desc: Put the clean cloth on the toilet tank

high_descs: turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn right and walk to the cabinet at the end of the room
grab a dirty wash cloth off of the lower left shelf of the cabinet
turn around and walk over to the sink up ahead at the end of the room
place the cloth inside of the sink and turn the water on, clean it off and then take it back out
turn around to face the toilet in the corner of the room
place the clean wash cloth on top of the back side of the toilet there
anns.task_desc: place a clean wash cloth on top of the back side of the toilet

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the dirty wash cloth near the floor that's furthest to the left.
Turn right and walk to the lip of the wall then turn right and walk to the sink and take a step to your right and walk to the wall then turn right to face the side of the sink.
Wash the dirty wash cloth in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around to face the toilet.
Put the wash cloth on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean wash cloth on the toilet.
